**Process Overview**

<img width="800" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000031-0/9DelRem.png"><br>

The process of delivery reminders requires the following steps:

1. Creation of terms and levels

2. Creation of reminders

3. Verification and posting of the reminders

4. Sending to vendors

Repeat steps 2 through 4 to send subsequent reminder levels.